 Image being unsupported, but I’m not sure about that either.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_FVTLH9AkAk0VYkXdsRT547CQ|fc_08ef2872fae49a900169fa652714e0819fa321efc6cf2290cf", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "rg \"accessDeclaredMembers|getDeclaredMethods\\(\\).*Security|fallsBackToPublicMethods\" tests/src -g'*.java' | head -100"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1395, "output": 2084, "cacheRead": 73728, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 77207, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1778017543933, "responseId": "resp_08ef2872fae49a900169fa65088a30819fa52580e10191b661"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_FVTLH9AkAk0VYkXdsRT547CQ|fc_08ef2872fae49a900169fa652714e0819fa321efc6cf2290cf", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "tests/src/net.sourceforge.htmlunit/htmlunit-core-js/2.70.0/src/test/java/net_sourceforge_htmlunit/htmlunit_core_js/JavaMembersTest.java:    void fallsBackToPublicMethodsWhenDeclaredMethodAccessIsDenied() {\ntests/src/net.sourceforge.htmlunit/htmlunit-core-js/2.70.0/src/test/java/net_sourceforge_htmlunit/htmlunit_core_js/JavaMembersTest.java:                    && \"accessDeclaredMembers\".equals(permission.getName())) {\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1778017575800}]}
