[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering class structure**\n\nI’m exploring options for resolving Object/String bootstrap. It seems I don't need a parent for an outer class unless it's loaded. Maybe it's better to avoid NestHost altogether and just use a simple top-level class. I could embed a class with an arbitrary name, but I’ll need to compile or generate it. Using an existing class could work, but if the parent is null, it might not load properly. If NestHost is required, I could run into a NoClassDefFoundError.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_08ef2872fae49a900169fa6563da6c819fac5e0f376430b440\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-mVwBQarBjyJgZfz4uUyIgvzx_vak6XD-7gt8iFcxXm7Xu_PzddH_NHQXGwgw6w0EV-ZxXcKKN8ugEnFc6V5SSPrPx8nsua73OrqPTBOardkthuiVKPyQQ2E5yCz7TwMfoLGoIpwsB6hust6sU39ZeR_9XGydnKUYsJ1LgEfSJgi0hubqeaRKWglcAYnxVCPDoMuox_l5BMW2RPHcjmwy8xvBEiXqVDMDnO5c_JTWlV6RZxceru2QbqcOyhMlKWOVaXHFvVdg_v7Y5W-wqb6ZUW0QLAsZS-IFVvsD0ucTldGpeXxKTZJYpuNZye5vEJtX81gE-cRV2qUt-PpFBxb51FMkKWIs_cGbVbM6thRUz2q7ojVkQgSikAVmaavSS6MSI7iBNVUjasWY8chZYQIh2wD01SGXLHA35yqrDAUGwfic2VR7JY-AbBZmwEyAYaC6HdRiLyau92nQtkANaFUE3TKHD8AmMZEPqhMYRmr8163RB-tY07jEXCrjGwLMmwS8Q44GUPSkqubng6QO2Vti3zp8-1SaCcmF4uVpJ9uwZXwMxqKKX7vs30xDgYQnn9rNxVvLP6Vb19sAAXybBOM5fywprlrFQy0bH1KYaVD80-bei5rjRkdx6_M_H7XIY1wUsegYNis-AAwAAkFn0vk7V70FDZH5UhGwNsHlBPyo1szCCF0rsEzJ489z966rcyy3Q8jVqtJYIM09t1keGcMaEA75OPZp6wU_ME3g_cuyTf0Gxa3EqPju-bevFCPYt8kXL4TS8tg7wPe2rLzBGqNx5Pq3yNrougKdmX1Cj2MTExuDnCsp8MyYAoBrKnP26Yu3zTYnImVqJIDpQ54WSlyM2NWmqdqAchzzwUdrbH1i3lMJ_-N79rLur5uZlaYZKMGL0a8XtxTyU-5H4Gy16RHwjS9P9ZX2ycZ_w46Vr8lRKjG2qCJiIE3UfaZLfUWdFtzj_ns5k45VS_Heg1W8JwtsUuyiiFfjgmRACMg3X9mQjD2ZbW3Yq0fMv5apj2glp9UlfHl8NuAcedgBh_ZsC0QIk-OV_soAT7StSI0ZYsiz_j7dFXSmVym3kEWeI9KGYJ7cXqbXfcRbGMS0JXezRxT29W9xTlpy3Dvi8ltSb7Wwu36OnWZVo9U4okF-UPVqjKOhTrrvSHbmnKcM62ZArP1msTZnSBvRv4pHUiq0pJRv5ObY4tsD9ibn9XxWLUWL8jKurmj8Jhq0l3NsOOWBXDmDlTGrjr7kKscsDCS